{"tid":122040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日見工火都黎","createTime":"2017-02-15T16:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T05:13:39.000Z","uid":66751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc221f23870737581f802d758077869af1036f21","tid":122040,"uid":66751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"話說今日去見份燒扒，咁我想趁住今年係2017年，慶祝我過左16歲可以返工，咪去學下點燒囉。咁我上到去就叫左個豬雞食，食完深思完得一個結論，呢間野黎返工好喇，食就真係最後一次算。食完就去同個收銀哥仔講想填form入職，唔洗兩分鐘個收銀帶我入房喎。問我：點解想做呢份工。咁我就話想賺啲零用養女囉。佢又再問幾時返到工，我話即時。戲肉就到，佢再問我有咩優點，我話我好叻，就考試都仲可以黎見工。佢55左我。戲肉到，佢問我點煮牛先可以有人性啲，我真係屌左岀聲，我話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇你煮咪最有人性囉</span>。佢唔岀聲，sd左張圖去我ws，我睇到真係忍得好辛苦，忍到啲屎都反沖上胃。最後，佢都係請左我，話等人洗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/005649_da6c24647096bdeaae40f991d57b933f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F005649_da6c24647096bdeaae40f991d57b933f.jpg&h=16554d3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d5c052dab06f9f814c258e6aa2d49ebbe686cd7","tid":122040,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:59:41.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"19aafd83edb946d98148433a70d9ecaa79d94898","tid":122040,"uid":66751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>0分重作</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acf996105d3e8017134f49ca7e252c77a00cff2","tid":122040,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png